title.narrative: Exchange rate impacts relevant to Danish Development Cooperation

description.narrative: Exchange rate impacts relevant to Danish Development Cooperation resulting from conversion to and from foreign currency in relation to transfers between accounts, receivables, and liabilities as well as regarding balances of cash in foreign bank accounts. The annual total exchange rate impacts can result in a net cost or a net benefit for the administrative expenses relevant to Danish Development Cooperation.
